</ul>
<h4><span>Reviewer's Spotlight Articles</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-4456">SCP-4456-D</a> (No One Expects The Spanish Decommission!) by Calibri bold - &quot;<em>After every reproduction random chimp event, the new SCP-4456 instance is to be provided with 2,500 pounds of pure silver.</em>&quot; - selected by <em>Calibri Bold</em></li>
</ul>
