<li><a href="/scp-o5-council-j">SCP-O5 Council-J</a> (<tt>&quot;The O5 Council&quot;</tt>) - This was coming, one day or another. Oh, and tha O5s are total living duds, lol. Written by cybersqyd.</li>
<li>📈 <a href="/scp-5650">SCP-5650</a> (&quot;To Cut Salmon by Its Angles&quot;) - All you need is a well-sharped knife. Written by Veralta.</li>
